或法庭之案底便不能被刪除（除非該罪犯上訴成功）。但根據《罪犯自新條例》（香港法例第297章）第2條，如罪犯是初犯者（即沒有其他案底），及被判處不超過3個月的監禁或罰款不超過10,000元，只要該罪犯在三年內不再犯案，其案底便可被視為「已喪失時效」。<br />\n<br />\n如案底已喪失時效，該罪犯等同沒有被定罪一樣，因此，如他在求職時被僱主或其他人詢問有無犯過刑事罪，他可立即回答：「無」。該人不得因為沒有披露其案底而被解僱。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"但要CHECK都CHECK都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fe6fc87001b64590e6563e558cafdfce9660c5","tid":691710,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99cf0cdcfde1442d539a218d422e96387560a298","tid":691710,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f264394d426cd2acbeb6f2071c7d147dce040ba9","tid":691710,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27689db311e8a367ff30e9ddf14b989fbeef2132","tid":691710,"uid":29784,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"bf99c3651eecbf7ce9f5c4c6e611f9e2d737fabd","tid":691710,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"衰乜？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"違反誠信既野<br />\n<br />\n假文書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"呃公司呃老闆先係違反誠信<br />\n呃朋友呃家人呃陌生人唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上網呃人十萬八萬個d好少要坐監<br />\n但呃公司三幾千都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61258218d297001953a1bc403446920277ee821a","tid":691710,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8897ae4795266f917d75342332124e906d38386b","tid":691710,"uid":150015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11fe6fc87001b64590e6563e558cafdfce9660c5","tid":691710,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3dca20ecbb6fea170c83cec1aaf3702a47db55e","tid":691710,"uid":